# corpus/ is intentionally NOT ignored: the seed corpus under
# corpus/ql_parse/ is committed (it mirrors the adversarial inputs in
# axil-ql/tests/comprehensive.rs). libFuzzer appends its own discovered inputs
# there at runtime; those extra files are harmless to leave uncommitted but are
# not auto-ignored so a contributor can choose to commit a reduced corpus.
